{"data":{"post":{"id":"914b5542-fb69-5024-821a-2a5861d16501","html":"<p>感谢贝贝提供插画(泡泡射手)           </p>\n<p><figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/2f957/bubble_shooter.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 95.89426321709787%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"bubble shooter\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/78f2b/bubble_shooter.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/dce19/bubble_shooter.jpg 200w,\n/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/c1413/bubble_shooter.jpg 400w,\n/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/78f2b/bubble_shooter.jpg 800w,\n/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/ab4c4/bubble_shooter.jpg 1200w,\n/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/bc99b/bubble_shooter.jpg 1600w,\n/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/2f957/bubble_shooter.jpg 1778w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>回想一下，在一个需要自我介绍的场景，你是如何自我介绍的？<br>\n<br>\n读书时，面对新同桌的自我介绍……<br>\n求职时，面对HR/Boss的自我介绍……<br>\n会友时，面对新朋友的自我介绍……               </p>\n<p>如何才能让大家记住你？<br>\n<br>\n猜名字游戏：<br>\n(一)<br>\n千千阙歌<br>\n神采奕奕<br>\n鹏程万里          </p>\n<p>(二)<br>\n引申触类<br>\n惊鸿艳影<br>\n百世流芬<br>\n<br>\n(三)<br>\n高大上<br>\n有作为<br>\n很安静<br>\n<br>\n(四)<br>\n海阔天高<br>\n宽大为怀<br>\n怡静体闲<br>\n<br>\n……<br>\n<br>\n换一种场景，面对自我介绍的对象：幼儿园中班的小朋友(开始认识字，特别爱打破沙锅问到底)<br>\nA: 这位是que叔叔……<br>\n中班小朋友贝贝： que叔叔？ 是麻雀的雀吗？<br>\n阙叔叔:啊哈哈……<br>\n……<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n</p>","fields":{"slug":"/how-to-introduce-yourself/","prefix":"2018-10-31"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to introduce yourself ?","author":"文:Jane 图(泡泡射手):贝贝","category":"funny","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/ada8c/bubble_shooter.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"e6ec6ad4-4c6b-586c-bfdf-8cdf2d09548f","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/how-to-introduce-yourself/","prev":{"id":"0b9d2c99-0be9-5867-b6fa-881264d12922","fields":{"slug":"/meditation/","prefix":"2018-10-30","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"瑜伽冥想引导词","category":"yoga"}},"next":{"id":"f7016fa5-6bea-5cb3-8bdf-c2e611d15cd9","fields":{"slug":"/study-hard-delicious-food/","prefix":"2018-11-04","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Study and food","category":"funny"}},"source":"posts"}}